gc.pmb_library.android.api.interfaces
Interface QuietTimeListener

public interface QuietTimeListener

The listener interface for receiving quietTime events. The class that is interested in processing a quietTime event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addQuietTimeListener method. When the quietTime event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked. This interface must be implemented to receive messages or the Quiet Time for the operations with the Quiettime.(set/get/delete Quiettime)
